Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:10.81,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.03,0:00:19.29,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.47,0:00:31.59,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:37.26,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The members of the Golden Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:40.18,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,who had reincarnated as \Nelves attacked the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:43.62,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, the Eye of the \NMidnight Sun's floating hideout arrived
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.62,0:00:45.60,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,at the royal capital,\Ncarrying Licht and Raia.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:50.23,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell invited that giant rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.69,0:00:53.99,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,But look. A pretty little \Nbird just showed up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.58,0:00:57.45,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Nozel and Noelle regrouped \Nwith Yami and the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:02.54,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,then split off in order to protect \Nthe people of the Clover Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:07.42,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But when Noelle and Nozel returned to the \NSilva residence, where they had grown up,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:11.17,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,they were faced with the \Nenemy's compass magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:15.13,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle used the experience she \Nhad gained in previous battles,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:17.89,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,as well as all the hours \Nshe'd spent training,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.89,0:01:23.70,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,along with her desire to save her \Nsiblings to gain new powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:27.48,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Now be destroyed! \NBoth you and this mad world!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:08.69,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Spatial Mage Brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.34,0:03:03.87,sign_12339_133_Finnes_Calmreich,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(1460,1)}Vermillion Residence
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:09.29,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times we blow \Nthis away, it comes right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.61,0:03:13.04,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,How dare those humans use \Nsuch impertinent spells?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:19.62,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,There are several enemies on the \Nthird floor and in the inner courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:23.45,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Which would mean the safest and most \Nbeautiful escape route would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.75,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:28.85,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:31.23,main,Noble,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mimosa and Kirsch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:32.66,main,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,You've saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:38.14,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Vermillion residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.14,0:03:41.75,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,The terrain is completely in our favor, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:44.05,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,My beautiful cherry blossom magic is helping
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:46.91,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,to confuse the enemy while \Nprotecting and hiding our allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:50.89,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,These shriveled little mushrooms \Nand their fungus magic weaken
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:52.92,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,the enemy's magic and \Ntheir ability to find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:56.69,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, my dear sister \NMimosa is using her plant magic
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:59.67,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,to search our residence \Nand guide us through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:04.07,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,If our goal is evacuation, \Nour spells are tailormade for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:06.19,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even have to worry about bloodshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.19,0:04:07.59,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,It's so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:09.52,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Please do shut up, Kirsch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.22,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,They'll find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:15.81,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,They're only our enemies because \Ntheir bodies were taken over by elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:18.21,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Members of the Golden Dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:22.22,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I promise you that we'll return you to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:24.99,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,Heya. Working hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.77,top,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,David!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:31.25,sign_6730_49_Captain_of_the_A,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Member of the Golden Dawn\N{\fs30}David Swallow
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:31.25,top,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,Nope! I'm Baval.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.59,0:04:34.32,italics,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't sense his presence at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.32,0:04:38.13,italics,En,0000,0000,0000,,How did he find us? \NOur spells aren't working?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:41.46,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on. Don't look so scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:45.19,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to interrupt when \Nyou were trying so hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:47.84,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,but all I did was find you and say hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:50.51,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,If I wanted to kill you, \Nyou'd all be dead by now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:52.73,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,so there's no point in getting all up in arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:55.42,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this elf?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:57.40,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,What are you after?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:04:59.13,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:01.86,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,Let's relax and have a little chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:07.04,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,I think you know this, but we've reincarnated \Nwith much more powerful magic than you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:10.07,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,and gathered here at the royals' residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:12.17,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,You can sense it, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:17.39,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,That there's powerful magic \Nother than ours heading here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:20.21,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's pointless to escape outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:22.67,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we're just going \Nto kill you all anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:25.87,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,So just relax and give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:29.18,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty amazing, but so are the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:33.60,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,Man... This really takes me back. \NI can't wait to see everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:35.60,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.97,0:05:37.90,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,We won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:42.19,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's fine and all, but I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:45.81,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,This match seems like it'll be over \Nas soon as the enemy's king is taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:51.85,sign_12339_133_Finnes_Calmreich,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(736,1042)}Kira Residence • Central Tower
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:50.49,top,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,There's a really powerful guy \Nvisiting your king right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:56.10,top,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,He's twisted, persistent, and stubborn, \Nso your king won't be able to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:57.33,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:06:03.59,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,If our guy uses {\i1}that{\i0} magic to kill,\N there's no way your king will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.37,0:06:10.51,italics,Vaude,0000,0000,0000,,My magic isn't enough to offset {\i0}that{\i1} magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:12.38,italics,Vaude,0000,0000,0000,,He's that powerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:17.93,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you?! What do you think \Nyou're doing in this sacred hall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.93,0:06:21.50,main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's the matter, Langris?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:25.86,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,That's the current king? \NHow seedy can a guy look?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:27.00,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Seedy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:30.39,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you call me seedy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:34.55,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,So your son is a traitorous rebel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:37.63,main,Vaude,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty, this is some kind of mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:42.12,main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes! My little Langris would \Nnever do something so fooli—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:43.19,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:47.38,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly... How could they \Nlet this scoundrel through?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:51.93,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Julius and the other Magic Knights \Nare all absolutely useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:56.68,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, scoundrel! \NI shall show you my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:03.96,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Behold my vast magical powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:07.28,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,You must be too busy shaking to even escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:09.14,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Light Magic:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.85,0:07:14.09,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Absolute Monarch of Divine Brilliance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:20.61,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like that?! Behold my godlike spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:24.39,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Now grovel before my authority!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:26.46,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:29.42,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,My spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:33.68,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,What a ridiculously slow light spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.60,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to kill you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:37.47,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start with your legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:39.52,main,Vaude,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:41.50,main,Vaude,0000,0000,0000,,Langris!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:46.90,main,Finnes,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't do this, Langris!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.44,main,Finnes,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't stop now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:56.37,main,Finnes,0000,0000,0000,,both you and the people who care \Nfor you are only going to be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:07:58.12,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:05.97,italics,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,You killed all of us elves, and you have \Nthe nerve to talk about being sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:13.38,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Langris!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:28.34,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Miss Finnes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:30.11,main,Finnes,0000,0000,0000,,Finral...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:31.78,main,Vaude,0000,0000,0000,,Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:34.03,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:38.16,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your older brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:41.79,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Stop trying to act cool, Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.07,0:08:45.29,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:47.46,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,What are the others doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:52.35,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We took care of all the other shiny guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:55.97,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,It would've gone more smoothly if \NMr. String Bean here had done his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:59.47,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,What? You were the one slacking off,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.47,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,you stupid meathead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:04.54,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you made a mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:08.47,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,in overestimating your strength \Nand splitting up your forces, elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:11.05,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,You expect me to believe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:14.61,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,Care to explain how you \Ntwo were able to beat them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:16.99,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Just like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:20.62,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We won't give you a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.16,italics,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,...to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.39,0:09:30.96,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. My magic seems to automatically
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:33.42,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,attack anyone who tries to attack me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:38.09,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,At least entertain me a little, humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:40.31,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:51.73,italics,Vaude,0000,0000,0000,,That level of spatial magic is astounding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:57.03,italics,Vaude,0000,0000,0000,,There's no spatial mage in this kingdom \Nwho can cancel a spell like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.52,0:09:59.88,italics,Vaude,0000,0000,0000,,And he has it protecting him \Nautomatically, at all times?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:02.30,italics,Vaude,0000,0000,0000,,No one could ask for a better shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:05.46,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Father, Miss Finnes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:08.01,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to us and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:09.83,main,Vaude,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:13.59,main,Vaude,0000,0000,0000,,You're just the Black Bulls' transport! \NYou don't stand a chance against Langris!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:16.11,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if I'm just \Nthe Black Bulls' transport,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:19.97,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,or if he's the Vice Captain \Nof the Golden Dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:22.85,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the only reason I'm fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:26.64,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,is because I'm his older brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:29.63,main,Vaude,0000,0000,0000,,Finral...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:34.63,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Could you not underestimate \Nmy squad's wheels?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:36.39,main,Vaude,0000,0000,0000,,What? Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:38.20,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're in the way, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:40.63,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Get moving, will ya, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.06,0:10:44.74,main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Langris! My dear little Langris!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:46.94,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you too, old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:49.86,main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Langris!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:54.15,main,Finnes,0000,0000,0000,,Finral, please come back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:57.26,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I will. Along with Langris.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.77,0:11:03.10,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:06.06,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you let me escape first?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:07.22,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:11.74,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, you're all worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:18.28,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, now. I still have \Nto tear you to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:19.74,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Langris...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:25.31,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like this kid's definitely \Ngonna be worth slashing apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:29.79,italics,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Severing Magic: Death Scythe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:31.50,italics,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Lunatic Slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:43.64,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid mantis!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.98,0:11:43.64,top,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Talk about an insane way \Nto help someone escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:45.77,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Just remember, he's the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:50.59,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,You gouged my slashes. Nice, very nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:52.27,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,He only sees the enemy now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:55.87,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,You still think you have \Na chance against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:12:00.94,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,Know your place, humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:05.29,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,He can actually use attack spells \Nwhile also using his automatic defense?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:06.87,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:10.16,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,If any of these hit you, \Nyou'll be dead instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:11.37,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,Spatial Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:12.91,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Spatial Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:14.92,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,Archangel's Crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:17.04,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Fallen Angel's Wingbeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:22.42,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,The difference in our \Nmagic power is too great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:25.72,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even block half of these with my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.64,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Avoid the rest any way you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:28.97,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.53,0:12:31.56,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you're \Nordering around, Finral?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:34.85,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Magic: Black Hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:39.98,italics,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Reinforcement Magic: Leg Strength Boost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:46.45,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Magic: Dark Cloaked \NLightless Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:48.53,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:52.66,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:59.06,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to do something \Nabout that defense
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:01.70,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,if we're gonna get anywhere near him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:07.15,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,But if he keeps attacking \Nus this relentlessly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:09.64,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Finral's magic won't be able\Nto keep canceling him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:14.58,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,A long battle puts us at a disadvantage. \NIf we start a fight, it needs to be quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:16.19,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to force our way through!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.02,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And for that to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:26.32,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We need more than one attack \Nto break through that defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:28.66,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I can take care of one side...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:32.24,italics,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had a prey like \Nthis in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:36.01,italics,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,I want to slash him... \NI want to slash him so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:37.50,italics,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Let me slash ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.99,0:13:42.06,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Jack's blades can cut \Nthrough all sorts of spells
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:47.51,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,by using his innate instincts to \Ntransform the very nature of his magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:51.81,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And all because he wants to slash things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:54.14,italics,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:59.13,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And even though spatial \Nmagic has unique properties,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:02.02,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,he's still able to slash through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:03.94,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.35,0:14:07.61,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And there he is! The tall, scrawny, \Nperverted weirdo genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:11.07,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Severing Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:12.74,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:14.54,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Cloaked...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:15.91,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:17.83,italics,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,...space!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:19.83,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Death Scythe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:21.33,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dimension Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:29.26,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:39.94,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Tch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:43.57,italics,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised that they were \Nable to get rid of my defenses,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:45.32,italics,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems they were one move short!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.02,0:14:51.99,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,You can't defend or even \Nattack with your spatial magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:55.37,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,My magic can't defeat my enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:14:58.25,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:02.67,italics,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,Return... to nothingness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:06.13,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Spatial Magic: Fallen Angel's Wingbeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.93,0:15:08.91,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:12.09,italics,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,He dropped his defenses so\Nhe could transport the others?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:21.57,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,My Fallen Angel's Wingbeat forcibly \Nmoves someone from one point to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.71,0:15:26.36,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save you along with my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:32.45,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad, human!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:35.36,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a little bit faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:37.29,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,You're all just going to die at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:41.53,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,These guys are Magic Knights Squad Captains!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:44.54,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,They'll do something about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:53.30,italics,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,The more I slash, the faster my blades become!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:57.10,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for your nap, little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.41,0:16:01.43,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Magic: Dark Cloaked \NLightless Blunt Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:05.19,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,This time, it should—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,0:16:09.53,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,You're just humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:13.53,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you do this to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:21.79,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,You petty... dirty, ugly humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:26.00,main,Latry,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.18,0:16:29.26,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Now he's really lost his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:34.13,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal with this \Nintensely wicked magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:35.01,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Tch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:38.25,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are we supposed \Nto do with this? Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:44.89,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,No... It's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:52.19,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,When he's that far gone, there's no\N way he'd notice my puny magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:57.49,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Langris...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.27,0:17:03.25,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking back, we've never actually \Nfought ever since we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:08.42,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I always ran away, using my \Nlack of talent as an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:13.19,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm your older brother, \Nand even though I realized you felt lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:18.66,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,This is... my last chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:23.31,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Your big brother's pretty confident \Nwhen it comes to agility and accuracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:27.27,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to stop you, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:33.53,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:34.98,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Langris!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:41.91,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Langris... Langris... Langris!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:43.83,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Langris!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:51.92,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,For the talented little brother, \Nyou sure are a handful. Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:58.93,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty weak, so... \NI'm sorry I took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:00.93,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Langris...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.65,0:18:21.32,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:24.41,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some nerve, taking all the \Nglory when you're nothing but a wimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:29.42,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Finral.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:37.58,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what I really want to \Nknow is... what's their endgame?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:41.46,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Are they gonna call it a day after \Nthey slaughter all us humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:45.26,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling they're \Nstill hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:50.87,italics,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,Finally... Soon, I'll be able \Nto see you awake, Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:58.99,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,Did you also just get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:03.01,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, that's not Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:05.70,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You're Patry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:09.24,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you always looked up to Licht,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:11.47,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,but you finally decided \Nto look like him, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.47,0:19:13.33,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "finally"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:17.46,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,When I reincarnated, I just \Nhappened to end up in this body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:20.15,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,This was my fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:22.21,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.21,0:19:23.39,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:26.72,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! It's been a while, Droit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.21,0:19:32.23,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I just reincarnated, so it doesn't \Nfeel like it's been that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:36.78,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Hey there, little Eclat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:38.18,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.18,0:19:40.55,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,Raia, where's Licht?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:42.74,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, good to see you, Patry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:45.06,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe because his body's artificial,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:49.75,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,or maybe because he's the one who activated \Nthe forbidden reincarnation spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.36,0:19:54.75,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,His memories aren't completely \Nback yet, and he's asleep right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:57.25,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:20:01.25,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Well, anyway, the gang's all here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:04.10,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else is waiting in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:06.01,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,We may all be here now,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:12.02,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm pretty sure the Golden Dawn's\Nalready taken care of all the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:14.92,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,There was a huge chunk \Ngouged out of the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:17.07,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Latry went a bit crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:20.17,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that seedy-looking king\N is no longer alive, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:23.32,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,Now all we have to do is fit the final
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:25.79,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,magic stone into the pedestal in the castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.79,0:20:29.37,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,and activate the spell that \Nuses the entire kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:33.57,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,That magic stone is \Nalready within our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:37.79,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,We'll wash away the malice \Nthat afflicts us as a side effect
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:39.21,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,of the forbidden spell,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:41.80,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,and complete our reincarnation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:44.63,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,We'll wipe out all of the humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.63,0:20:48.78,main,Patrlicht,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll take back this world, \Nmaking it a peaceful world for elves alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.53,0:21:01.78,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bet that there are a \Nbunch of tough guys in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:07.62,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what the rest of my dumbasses \Nand the other Magic Knights are doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:11.16,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna flatten all the elves \Nmyself if they don't get here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:13.10,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'm gonna slash 'em all first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:14.42,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,No, it'll be me.
