Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.98,0:22:49.15,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.09,0:22:54.10,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:52.50,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.10,0:22:57.64,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna flatten all the elves \Nmyself if they don't get here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:22:59.87,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'm gonna slash 'em all first.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.87,0:23:01.23,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,No, it'll be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.23,0:23:02.49,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,No, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.02,0:23:05.66,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I'm gonna kick all their asses!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.66,0:23:08.40,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm telling you that {\i1}I'm{\i0} \Ngonna kick all their asses!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.40,0:23:09.72,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,No, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.72,0:23:12.66,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Me, me, me, me, me, me, me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:14.13,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.26,0:23:17.87,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Tch! You piss me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:21.25,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop copying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:22.18,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.18,0:23:24.71,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,I said stop copying me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.71,0:23:25.51,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.66,0:23:29.97,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.97,0:23:32.21,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We keep doing the same things!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.21,0:23:35.95,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,After all's said and done,\NYami and Jack are totally in sync.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.95,0:23:37.30,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.86,0:23:42.55,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,My beautiful voice, my beautiful flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.55,0:23:46.19,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Everything about me, \NKirsch "Beautiful" Vermillion, is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.19,0:23:50.15,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 110: \N"The Raging Bull Joins the Showdown!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.94,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 110\N\N{\fs18} The Raging Bull Joins the Showdown!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.15,0:23:54.07,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,I am not a raging bull. \NI'm just ragingly beautiful!
